{"title":"TailWind CSS 安裝使用","uid":"34c374d5f6028d6959470611bd751584","slug":"TWCSS01 【TailWind CSS 安裝使用】","date":"2023-12-05T10:42:08.000Z","updated":"2024-02-15T14:07:59.383Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/TWCSS01 【TailWind CSS 安裝使用】.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://github.com/HSU0201/images/blob/main/tailwindcss/b4fd5300-b585-11ea-8718-1e141e78842e.png?raw=true","content":"<h1 id=\"01-【TailWind-CSS-安裝使用】\"><a href=\"#01-【TailWind-CSS-安裝使用】\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"01 【TailWind CSS 安裝使用】\"></a>01 【TailWind CSS 安裝使用】</h1><blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p><strong>簡介：</strong>Tailwind CSS 是一個功能類優先的 CSS 框架，它整合了諸如 flex, pt-4, text-center 和 rotate-90 這樣的的類，它們能直接在腳本標記語言中組合起來，建構出任何設計。</p></blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"1-方法一-使用-CDN-快速體驗-Tailwind-CSS\"><a href=\"#1-方法一-使用-CDN-快速體驗-Tailwind-CSS\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1. [方法一] 使用 CDN 快速體驗 Tailwind CSS\"></a>1. [方法一] 使用 CDN 快速體驗 Tailwind CSS</h2><blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>使用 Play CDN 直接在瀏覽器中試用 Tailwind，無需任何建構步驟。Play CDN 僅用於開發目的，不是生産的最佳選擇。</p></blockquote>\n<p>將 Play CDN 腳本標記加入到 HTML 文件的 ，然後開始使用 Tailwind 的實用工具類來設定內容的樣式。<code>&lt;head&gt;</code></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">&lt;!DOCTYPE <span class=\"keyword\">html</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">html</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">head</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">meta</span> <span class=\"attr\">charset</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;UTF-8&quot;</span> /&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">meta</span> <span class=\"attr\">name</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;viewport&quot;</span> <span class=\"attr\">content</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0&quot;</span> /&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\">&lt;!-- Play CDN --&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">script</span> <span class=\"attr\">src</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;https://cdn.tailwindcss.com&quot;</span>&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">script</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">head</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">body</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">div</span> <span class=\"attr\">class</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;flex&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">      <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">div</span> <span class=\"attr\">class</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;flex-none w-14 h-14 bg-pink-500&quot;</span>&gt;</span>1<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">      <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">div</span> <span class=\"attr\">class</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;flex-initial w-64 bg-red-700&quot;</span>&gt;</span>2<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">      <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">div</span> <span class=\"attr\">class</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;flex-initial w-32 bg-green-50&quot;</span>&gt;</span>3<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">body</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">html</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h2 id=\"2-方法二-使用-npm-安裝-Tailwind-CSS\"><a href=\"#2-方法二-使用-npm-安裝-Tailwind-CSS\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2. [方法二] 使用 npm 安裝 Tailwind CSS\"></a>2. [方法二] 使用 npm 安裝 Tailwind CSS</h2><p><strong>第一步：安裝 Tailwind CSS</strong></p>\n<p>安裝 <code>Tailwind CSS</code> 並創建 <code>tailwind.config.js</code> 配置文件</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta prompt_\"># </span><span class=\"language-bash\">建立一個名為 demo 的資料夾</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">mkdir demo</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta prompt_\"># </span><span class=\"language-bash\">進入 demo 資料夾</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">cd demo</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta prompt_\"></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta prompt_\"># </span><span class=\"language-bash\">安裝 Tailwind CSS，-D 參數表示將其作為開發相依性安裝</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">npm install -D tailwindcss</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta prompt_\"># </span><span class=\"language-bash\">初始化，此命令會生成 tailwind.config.js 配置檔</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">npx tailwindcss init</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>1）npm install -D tailwindcss 會生成文件及目錄</p>\n<p>node_modules package-lock.json package.json</p>\n<p>2）npx tailwindcss init 生成如下配置文件</p>\n<p>tailwind.config.js</p></blockquote>\n<p><strong>第二步：編輯 tailwind.config.js 配置文件</strong></p>\n<p>加入文件到配置文件中</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight js\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"variable language_\">module</span>.<span class=\"property\">exports</span> = &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"comment\">// content 欄位指定需要掃描的檔案，以提取樣式</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"comment\">// 會掃描 ./src 目錄下的所有 HTML 和 JavaScript 檔案</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attr\">content</span>: [<span class=\"string\">&quot;./src/**/*.&#123;html,js&#125;&quot;</span>],</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"comment\">// theme 欄位用於定義主題，包括顏色、字型大小等</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"comment\">// 在這個例子中，extend 欄位是空的，表示沒有對主題進行額外的擴展。</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attr\">theme</span>: &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\">// extend 欄位允許你在已有主題的基礎上進行擴展</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attr\">extend</span>: &#123;&#125;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">  &#125;,</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"comment\">// plugins 欄位用於配置外掛程式</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"comment\">// 外掛程式陣列是空的，表示沒有額外的外掛程式被配置</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attr\">plugins</span>: [],</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><strong>第三步：加入 Tailwind 樣式指令到 CSS 文件中</strong></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight css\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">/* 引入 Tailwind CSS 的基本樣式 */</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">@tailwind</span> base;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">/* 引入 Tailwind CSS 的元件樣式 */</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">@tailwind</span> components;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">/* 引入 Tailwind CSS 的實用程式類別 */</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">@tailwind</span> utilities;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>**@tailwind base;**：<br>這將引入 Tailwind CSS 的基本樣式，通常包括一些重置樣式和一般的 HTML 元素樣式。</p>\n<p>**@tailwind components;**：<br>這將引入 Tailwind CSS 的元件樣式，包括預製的元件樣式，如按鈕、卡片等。</p>\n<p>**@tailwind utilities;**：<br>這將引入 Tailwind CSS 的實用程式類別，這是 Tailwind 的強大之處，提供了大量的快速實用的樣式類別，用於調整元素的外觀和排版。</p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>若有警告的在 vscode 中安裝<code>PostCSS Language Support</code>插件</p></blockquote>\n<p><strong>第四步：npm init -y</strong></p>\n<p><strong>第五步：使用 Tailwind Cli 建構 CSS 樣式</strong></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npx tailwindcss -i ./src/input.css -o ./dist/output.css --watch</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>該指令會將 <code>src/style.css</code> 中 <code>Tailwind CSS</code> 編譯到 <code>demo/dist/mystyle.css</code> 文件中，<code>mystyle.css</code> 就是編譯後樣式，項目中引入的就是它。</p>\n<p>現在打開 <code>package.json</code> 文件，加入以下執行腳本：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight json\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">&quot;scripts&quot;</span><span class=\"punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"punctuation\">&#123;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attr\">&quot;build&quot;</span><span class=\"punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"string\">&quot;tailwindcss -i ./src/style.css -o ./dist/output.css --watch&quot;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"punctuation\">&#125;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>這時候只要執行<code>npm run build</code>就可以自動監聽你的頁面改動並且實時編譯了。</p>\n<p><strong>第六步：小試牛刀</strong></p>\n<p>經過上面 4 個小步驟，<code>Tailwind CSS</code> 就已經安裝好，下面就來瞅瞅。</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">&lt;!DOCTYPE <span class=\"keyword\">html</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">html</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">head</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">meta</span> <span class=\"attr\">charset</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;UTF-8&quot;</span> /&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">meta</span> <span class=\"attr\">name</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;viewport&quot;</span> <span class=\"attr\">content</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0&quot;</span> /&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">link</span> <span class=\"attr\">href</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;/dist/output.css&quot;</span> <span class=\"attr\">rel</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;stylesheet&quot;</span> /&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">head</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">body</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">h1</span> <span class=\"attr\">class</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;text-3xl font-bold underline&quot;</span>&gt;</span>Hello world!<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">h1</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">body</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">html</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><h3 id=\"題外補充-自動重新整理-HTML-文件\"><a href=\"#題外補充-自動重新整理-HTML-文件\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"(題外補充) 自動重新整理 HTML 文件\"></a>(題外補充) 自動重新整理 HTML 文件</h3><p>不屬於 Tailwind CSS 的範疇，如果在寫靜態頁面的時候，需要每次修改 html 頁面，瀏覽器就自動重新整理這個頁面，那麼只需要在 vscode 內搜索<code>Live Preview</code>並且安裝，之後在你需要預覽的頁面，右鍵，選擇<code>Live Preview：Show Preview</code>即可。</p></blockquote>\n","feature":null,"text":"A abstracts of what this article is about....","permalink":"/post/TWCSS01 【TailWind CSS 安裝使用】","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"3.4k","symbolsTime":"3 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"TailWind CSS","slug":"TailWind-CSS","count":1,"path":"api/categories/TailWind-CSS.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"CSS","slug":"CSS","count":9,"path":"api/tags/CSS.json"},{"name":"TailWind CSS","slug":"TailWind-CSS","count":1,"path":"api/tags/TailWind-CSS.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#01-%E3%80%90TailWind-CSS-%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%9D%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E3%80%91\"><span class=\"toc-text\">01 【TailWind CSS 安裝使用】</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#1-%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%E4%B8%80-%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8-CDN-%E5%BF%AB%E9%80%9F%E9%AB%94%E9%A9%97-Tailwind-CSS\"><span class=\"toc-text\">1. [方法一] 使用 CDN 快速體驗 Tailwind CSS</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#2-%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%E4%BA%8C-%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8-npm-%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%9D-Tailwind-CSS\"><span class=\"toc-text\">2. [方法二] 使用 npm 安裝 Tailwind CSS</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E9%A1%8C%E5%A4%96%E8%A3%9C%E5%85%85-%E8%87%AA%E5%8B%95%E9%87%8D%E6%96%B0%E6%95%B4%E7%90%86-HTML-%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6\"><span class=\"toc-text\">(題外補充) 自動重新整理 HTML 文件</span></a></li></ol></li></ol></li></ol>","author":{"name":"Hsu's Blog","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://github.com/HSU0201/images/blob/main/blogimage.jpg?raw=true","link":"/","description":"“Stay cur